The aim of this course is to provide learners with a framework for the necessary thought and exercise materials for conducting a theater class. We will start by classifying exercise materials and developing an initial network of exercises to use in theater class. The second half of the course will focus on designing exercise materials specific to individual learners' work.Objectives/eesmärkid:  To introduce, analyze, and develop the necessary exercises and techniques for conducting a theater class.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  Upon completion of the course, the learner will be able to:
Select and create appropriate exercises for conducting a theater class;
Design exercises specific to their own work;
Translate theoretical knowledge into practical exercises.
